{"tid":1662710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方: 段崇智信件連最基本資料也看不到","createTime":"2019-10-19T02:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T13:13:13.000Z","uid":7971,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"55dbe62c130552aca477e1fe64eb17e1ab747cc7","tid":1662710,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"中大校長段崇智發出公開信，表示多名被捕同學表示，曾遭遇警方一種或多種不同程度的不合理對待。他說，對於部分警務人員涉嫌不當使用暴力或違反人權，經查證後須予以譴責。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科署理總警司江永祥表示，任何人如對警方行動或拘捕過程有不滿，覺得受屈辱，應挺身而出投訴並提供資料。他說，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">在段崇智信件中，連最基本的資料也看不到，而各類調查中最重要的拼圖是當事人口供。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n江永祥表示，看到聲稱受屈辱的人士，每次出來說話的內容都有少許不同，增加警方跟進難度，不知道哪一次所說的才是事實的全部。他說，即使警方有任何基本資料可作跟進，最後若投訴人不願挺身而出，都不能還原真相，對任何方面都不公平。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486976-20191018.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486976-20191018.htm&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9pgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=f5fdbe84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486976-20191018.htm&h=171ef00a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486976-20191018.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6e3b58799261f26f0cddf50f05f09f82577561e0","tid":1662710,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T02:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fi1xkop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFi1xkop.jpg&h=a8433196&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a3a615b818f25c33dc73e37cd962c2594bc7df4","tid":1662710,"uid":7971,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T02:48:00.000Z","msg":"一間大學校長嘅聲明 都可以被警方wfc"},{"pid":"6aae2f33a25b56670dcecfa67da5520980264a0e","tid":1662710,"uid":522,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"8a3a615b818f25c33dc73e37cd962c2594bc7df4","tid":1662710,"uid":7971,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"cit